mindmap
  root((Text Cleaning Logic))
    Step 1: Extract Base
      Use dotall modifier
      Catch multiline <h1>
    Step 2: Strip Tags
      Find anything inside <>
      Replace with empty string
    Step 3: Decode
      Convert HTML entities
      &amp; becomes &
    Step 4: Normalize
      Remove tabs
      Remove newlines
      Single space format
    Step 5: OS Safety
      No slashes
      No colons
      Max length 60